  <div class="row">
    <div class="medium-12 columns">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <%= nested_menu_items(menu_items: @footer_menu.menu_items) %>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        May Williams LLP (registered in England and Wales OC123456) is authorised
        and regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority (number 5222333).
        Our registered office is No. 1 London Bridge, London, SE1 9BG.
        The term ‘partner’ is used to refer to a member of the partnership or to an
        employee of equivalent standing and qualifications. May Williams LLP
        provides its services subject to its Terms of Business, a copy of which is
        available on request.
      </p>
    </div>
